---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="CV · dotMavriQ" description="Curriculum Vitae of Jonatan Jansson (dotMavriQ)">
  <article class="relative z-30 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-10 md:py-14">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-gruv-fg text-gruv-bg/95 shadow-md shadow-black/30 border border-gruv-surface overflow-hidden p-6 md:p-10 relative">
      <header class="mb-10 flex flex-col gap-6 md:gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-end">
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-3">
          <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Jonatan Jansson</h1>
          <div class="text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-relaxed font-medium space-y-1">
            <p>Lisbon Area, Portugal</p>
            <p>
              <span class="mr-1 align-middle opacity-80 text-[13px]" aria-hidden="true">✉</span>
              <a href="mailto:social@dotmavriq.life" class="underline decoration-dashed decoration-gruv-bg/40 underline-offset-2 text-[#076678] hover:text-[#458588] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#458588] rounded-sm">social@dotmavriq.life</a>
            </p>
            <p class="flex items-center gap-1.5 group">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256" width="14" height="14" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" class="opacity-80 text-[#076678] group-hover:text-[#458588] transition-colors">
                <g transform="scale(5.12)">
                  <path fill="currentColor" d="M41,4h-32c-2.76,0 -5,2.24 -5,5v32c0,2.76 2.24,5 5,5h32c2.76,0 5,-2.24 5,-5v-32c0,-2.76 -2.24,-5 -5,-5zM17,20v19h-6v-19zM11,14.47c0,-1.4 1.2,-2.47 3,-2.47c1.8,0 2.93,1.07 3,2.47c0,1.4 -1.12,2.53 -3,2.53c-1.8,0 -3,-1.13 -3,-2.53zM39,39h-6c0,0 0,-9.26 0,-10c0,-2 -1,-4 -3.5,-4.04h-0.08c-2.42,0 -3.42,2.06 -3.42,4.04c0,0.91 0,10 0,10h-6v-19h6v2.56c0,0 1.93,-2.56 5.81,-2.56c3.97,0 7.19,2.73 7.19,8.26z" />
                </g>
              </svg>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/janssonjonatan/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="underline decoration-dashed decoration-gruv-bg/40 underline-offset-2 text-[#076678] group-hover:text-[#458588] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#458588] rounded-sm">linkedin.com/in/janssonjonatan</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start md:items-end gap-2 text-sm md:text-xs font-mono">
          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 md:top-5 md:right-5 flex flex-col items-end gap-1">
            <a href="/site_icons/jonatanjanssonCVSep2025.pdf" download="JonatanJansson-CV-Sep-2025.pdf" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-gruv-bg/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-gruv-bg/30 hover:bg-gruv-bg/20 hover:border-gruv-bg/40 text-gruv-bg font-medium tracking-tight shadow shadow-black/20 transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gruv-yellow/40">
              <span>Download PDF</span>
            </a>
            <span class="text-gruv-bg/60">Updated Sep 2025</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- SUMMARY / SKILLS INTRO -->
      <section id="skills" class="space-y-6 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Skills</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
          <p>Skilled professional with extensive experience in web development, technical support, and system configuration. Strong communication and customer collaboration skills; adept at integrating feedback and ensuring reliable, maintainable solutions.</p>
          <p>Hands-on across front-end and back-end (JavaScript, PHP, Python) with specialization in WordPress & WooCommerce ecosystems and adjacent CMS platforms (Joomla, Magento). Experienced in performance tuning, marketing‑focused development, copywriting, content management, and iterative optimization of digital properties.</p>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Key Skills</h3>
            <ul class="grid gap-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 text-sm md:text-[13px] font-mono">
              <li>JavaScript / TypeScript (ESNext)</li>
              <li>React & Modern Frontend</li>
              <li>WordPress (Plugins / Themes / Woo)</li>
              <li>Headless & API Integration</li>
              <li>Performance (Core Web Vitals)</li>
              <li>Accessibility (WCAG 2.2)</li>
              <li>Technical SEO / Structured Data</li>
              <li>Growth Engineering / A/B Testing</li>
              <li>Marketing Automation (HubSpot)</li>
              <li>Analytics & Tag Management (GA4)</li>
              <li>AI Integration (OpenAI APIs)</li>
              <li>PHP / Python / Shell Scripting</li>
              <li>Docker / GitHub Actions / CDN</li>
              <li>Security (OWASP basics)</li>
              <li>Testing (Playwright / Selenium)</li>
              <li>Observability & Monitoring</li>
              <li>CMS Workflow & Editorial Tooling</li>
              <li>Data Integration & Automation</li>
              <li>API Design & Consumption</li>
              <li>Documentation & Enablement</li>
              <li>Stakeholder Alignment</li>
              <li>Localization / i18n</li>
              <li>Version Control & Code Review</li>
              <li>Linux Systems & Server Hardening</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- EXPERIENCE (timeline styled) -->
      <section id="experience" class="mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Experience</h2>
        <div class="relative pl-8 md:pl-10">
          <!-- vertical line -->
          <div class="absolute left-2.5 md:left-3 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gruv-bg/30"></div>
          <div class="space-y-12">
            <div class="relative">
              <span class="absolute -left-6 md:-left-7 top-2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gruv-bg ring-2 ring-gruv-fg shadow shadow-black/30"></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Nordhealth — Senior Growth Developer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2025 – Present</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Lead development & optimization of multi‑market WordPress product / marketing sites.</li>
                <li>Improve conversions & performance (Core Web Vitals, A/B testing, caching, asset strategy).</li>
                <li>Consolidate legacy properties into a unified platform & design system.</li>
                <li>Integrate AI‑assisted workflows & content automation to accelerate funnel growth.</li>
                <li>Implement security hardening, analytics / tag & CRM integrations, deploy pipelines.</li>
                <li>Partner with marketing on rapid experiments & high‑impact feature launches.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <span class="absolute -left-6 md:-left-7 top-2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gruv-bg ring-2 ring-gruv-fg shadow shadow-black/30"></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Block Labs LTD, Lisbon — WordPress Developer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2024 – 2025</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Develop high‑performance WordPress sites (custom themes & plugins).</li>
                <li>Design architecture & manage advanced CMS configurations.</li>
                <li>Implement DB & server integrations for enterprise solutions.</li>
                <li>Performance testing, troubleshooting & continuous optimization.</li>
                <li>Collaborate cross‑functionally to meet business objectives.</li>
                <li>Lead enterprise server migrations and platform hardening.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <span class="absolute -left-6 md:-left-7 top-2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gruv-bg ring-2 ring-gruv-fg shadow shadow-black/30"></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">IPTOR, Lisbon — WordPress Developer</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2023 – 2024</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Built enterprise WordPress plugin integrating TeamTailor API.</li>
                <li>Maintained GENII Group properties focusing on performance & UX.</li>
                <li>Implemented technical solutions supporting inbound marketing.</li>
                <li>Expanded HubSpot & adjacent MarTech integration expertise.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="relative">
              <span class="absolute -left-6 md:-left-7 top-2 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gruv-bg ring-2 ring-gruv-fg shadow shadow-black/30"></span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Duva, Lidköping — Web Developer / Software Tester / Support</h3>
              <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2018 – 2023</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                <li>Delivered front‑end builds for 50+ clients (WordPress, HTML, CSS, JS, PHP).</li>
                <li>Consulted on performance, resilience & troubleshooting for enterprise sites.</li>
                <li>Planned and refined solutions with international stakeholders.</li>
                <li>Executed systematic software testing & debugging for stable releases.</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase text-gruv-bg/70">Key Projects</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-1 text-[14px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                  <li><strong>Monokel</strong> — Support, system administration, customer relations; managed integrations & client communication loops.</li>
                  <li><strong>1Sekund</strong> — Marketing & system admin; platform visibility & content operations.</li>
                  <li><strong>McKonsult</strong> — Developed Parts Europe integrations; authored site content & product copy.</li>
                  <li><strong>Ulricehamns Municipality</strong> — Technical consultant & integration manager for health inquiry workflows.</li>
                  <li><strong>24-sju.se</strong> — E‑commerce improvements & franchise support.</li>
                  <li><strong>Academedia</strong> — WordPress dev (themes, plugins, DB), cross‑team integration & stability improvements.</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ADDITIONAL EXPERIENCE -->
      <section id="additional-experience" class="space-y-8 mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Additional Experience</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Lidköping Makerspace, Sweden — Founder</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2017 – 2019</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Founded and operated local makerspace; sourced equipment & negotiated spaces.</li>
              <li>Built partnerships with governmental bodies, NGOs & think tanks.</li>
              <li>Established NGO chapter with 20+ members; provided web support.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Ember, Lidköping — Internship</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2017</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Handled inbound support & clerical processes.</li>
              <li>Malware remediation & security hardening for local client systems.</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-3 space-y-2">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm tracking-wide uppercase text-gruv-bg/70">Key Projects</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-[14px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
                <li><strong>Incup</strong> — Remote desktop administration for 50+ client environments ensuring availability, updates & incident response.</li>
                <li><strong>Assemblin</strong> — Authored PowerShell automation scripts to audit commercial vehicle movement data and streamline reporting.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Nordic Goods AB — Contractor / SysAdmin / Developer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2016</p>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-[15px] leading-snug list-disc list-inside">
              <li>Launched e‑commerce sites & digital campaigns from scratch.</li>
              <li>Full‑stack development, system administration & industry partnerships.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- EDUCATION -->
      <section id="education" class="space-y-8 mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Education</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Lexicon, Skövde — Certificate of Achievement</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">Nov 2015 – Feb 2016</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Web Application Development with C# (.NET / Visual Studio): ASP.NET debugging, database management, MVC site architecture, testing practices.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">De La Gardie, Lidköping — Technical Program (IT)</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-mono text-gruv-bg/70">2008 – 2011</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Core IT fundamentals: programming, systems, database concepts & applied computing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- AWARDS -->
      <section id="awards" class="space-y-4 mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Awards</h2>
        <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">UF‑Mässan, Vara — Silver Medalist (2011)</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">Silver Medal for Best Youth Start‑up: Muciety.com forum aggregator & social network for musicians.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- LANGUAGE -->
      <section id="language" class="space-y-4 mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Language</h2>
        <ul class="text-[15px] leading-snug space-y-1">
          <li>🇸🇪 Swedish — Native</li>
          <li>🇬🇧 English — Native</li>
          <li>🇵🇹 Portuguese (PT-pt) — A2 Level</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- CERTIFICATIONS -->
      <section id="certifications" class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Additional Certifications</h2>
        <ol class="text-[15px] leading-snug space-y-1 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li>Full Stack Developer – LinkedIn Learning Path (2025)</li>
          <li>Google Digital Garage – Fundamentals of Digital Marketing (2023)</li>
          <li>HubSpot Academy – Inbound (2023)</li>
          <li>NDG Linux Unhatched (2023)</li>
          <li>Linux Foundation – LFS101 Foundations in Linux (2014)</li>
          <li>Certificate of Achievement – .NET Systems Developer Course (2015)</li>
          <li>Moz – Advanced SEO: Tactics and Strategy (2015)</li>
          <li>WordPress: SEO – LinkedIn (2024)</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
